{"tid":1681791,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"示威者侮辱國旗判服務令　梁振英：引起全國公憤律政司必須上訴","createTime":"2019-10-29T15:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T15:56:50.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c61fda4bf5be3754aff8130e1c8660a89c03c886","tid":1681791,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191029/_2019102922553023040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191029%2F_2019102922553023040.jpg&h=29996aeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁振英批評判刑過低。資料圖片<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191029/_2019102922532043923.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191029%2F_2019102922532043923.jpg&h=78d1af2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n示威者扯下國旗丟入城門河。資料圖片<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191029/_2019102922531786207.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191029%2F_2019102922531786207.jpg&h=5fc2b0e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學生包圍知專院長乘坐的救護車。資料圖片<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191029/_2019102922532249455.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191029%2F_2019102922532249455.jpg&h=add2ad1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田示威者扯下國旗踐踏塗黑撕毀丟入城門河。資料圖片<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191029/_2019102922531928256.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191029%2F_2019102922531928256.jpg&h=9b583ae1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田示威者扯下國旗踐踏塗黑撕毀丟入城門河。資料圖片<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191029/_2019102922532154309.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191029%2F_2019102922532154309.jpg&h=bfcd8bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田示威者扯下國旗踐踏塗黑撕毀丟入城門河。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n前行政長官、全國政協副主席梁振英在社交網站回應一宗侮辱國旗案件時，指「一名狂徒上月在沙田涉嫌踐踏國旗並棄於城門河，今日在沙田裁判法院被判200小時社會服務令。這判決必定引起全國公憤，既然裁判官表示沒有量刑指引，律政司必須上訴」。他又提到，早前有人塗污美國總領事館外牆，被判刑四個星期。<br />\n<br />\n他又提到，知專設計學院15歲女學生陳彥霖浮屍事件，指有學生繼續逼迫學院院長王麗蓮和副院長黃偉祖。他形容，「我看了電視新聞的畫面，總覺得蒙面的黑衣人就是中東的恐怖分子，院長和副院長就是人質，恐怖分子將刀架在人質的頸上，迫人質對著鏡頭讀出譴責這個哪個的聲明」。<br />\n<br />\n9月22日有網民號召「和你shop」到商場示威，沙田新城市廣場有大批示威者聚集唱歌及呼叫口號，有示威者拆下國旗將之塗黑及踐踏，再將國旗扔進垃圾車內再推落城門河。21歲技工早前承認一項侮辱國旗罪，今在沙田裁判法院被判200小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1624641/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E4%BE%AE%E8%BE%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%97%97%E5%88%A4%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E4%BB%A4-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1-%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%AC%E6%86%A4%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E5%BF%85%E9%A0%88%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1624641%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2597%2597%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%2586%25A4%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E5%25BF%2585%25E9%25A0%2588%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=8e453761\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1624641%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E4%25BE%25AE%25E8%25BE%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2597%2597%25E5%2588%25A4%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E4%25BB%25A4-%2